OL,3,CReform UK takes control of Newcastle-
OL,4,Cunder-Lyme borough
OL,6,FSupport for Reform UK has surged in
OL,7,FNewcastle-Under-Lyme borough, with the
OL,8,Fparty winning control of the council
OL,9,Ffrom the Conservatives.
OL,11,FIt is the party's first win that has
OL,12,Fbeen announced so far in the 2026
OL,13,Flocal elections.
OL,15,FWith all the council's 44 seats
OL,16,Fcontested, ballots were counted
OL,17,Fovernight at Keele University sports
OL,18,Fcentre.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
