OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1778242270
OL,3,CReform UK takes control of Newcastle-
OL,4,Cunder-Lyme borough
OL,6,FMartin Rogerson, Reform UK branch
OL,7,Fchairman for Newcastle-under-Lyme,
OL,8,Fsaid: "I would like to thank everyone
OL,9,Fwho made the commitment to stand in
OL,10,Fthis election, and all those who have
OL,11,Fworked to make it possible.
OL,13,F"We are delighted and humbled that
OL,14,Fpeople have placed their trust in us
OL,15,Fand I promise that we will get to work
OL,16,Fstraightaway delivering local
OL,17,Fservices."
OL,26,@yD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
