PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1778242270
OL,3,CReform UK takes control of Newcastle-
OL,4,Cunder-Lyme borough
OL,6,FIn Lincoln, Labour retained control of
OL,7,Fthe city council, getting the 17 seats
OL,8,Fit needed, but losing three to Reform,
OL,9,FLiberal Democrats and the Green Party.
OL,10,FThe Conservatives lost three of their
OL,11,Fseats to Reform.
OL,13,FReform made gains elsewhere too - four
OL,14,Fseats in Peterborough, making them the
OL,15,Fsecond largest party there. But the
OL,16,Fcouncil there remains hung.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
